\c 11
\p
\v 1 Chiyero chinonyengedzera chi nonyangadza kuna Jehovha; Asi kurema kwakakwana kunomufadza.
\v 2 Kana kuzvikudza kuchisvika, kunyadziswa kwasvikawo; Asi uchenjeri huri kuna vanozvininipisa.
\v 3 Kusanyengedzera kwavakarurama kuchavatungamirira; Asi kusarurama kwavanonyengedzera kuchaparadza.
\v 4 Pfuma haibatsiri chinhu nezuva rokutsamwa; Asi kururama kunorwira parufu.
\v 5 Kururama kwowakakwana kucharuramisa nzira yake;
\s Asi wakaipa uchawiswa nezvakaipa zvake.
\p
\v 6 Kururama kwavakarurama kuchavarwira;
\s Asi vanonyengedzera vachabatwa nezvakashata zvavo.
\p
\v 7 Kana munhu wakaipa achifa, zvaanotarira zvichaparadzwa; Tariro yavakashata inoparadzwa.
\p
\v 8 Wakarurama anorwirwa pakutambudzika;
\p Wakaipa anopinda pachigaro chake.
\v 9 Wakashata anoparadza wokwake nomuromo wake;
\p Asi wakarurama acharwirwa nezivo.
\v 1 ° Kana vakarurama vachipfuurira mberi zvakanaka,
\s guta rinofara kwazvo;
\s Kana vakaipa vachiparadzwa, kunopururudzwa.
\s Nokuropafadzwa kwavakarurama guta rinokudzwa;
\s Asi rinoputswa nemiromo
\s yavakaipa.
\p
\v 12 Anoninipisa wokwake anoshaiwa uchenjeri;
\s Asi munhu ane njere anoramba anyerere.
\p
\v 13 Anofamba ana makuhwa,
\s anobudisa zvakavanda;
\s Asi ano mwoyo wakatendeka, anofukidza mhaka.
\p
\v 14 Kana vanhu vasingatungamirirwi
\s nouchenjeri, vanoderera;
\s Asi pavarairiri vazhinji ndipo pano ruponeso.
\s is Wakazviita rubatso pamusoro pomutorwa,
\s achaona nhamo nokuda kwazvo; Asi anovenga kuzviita rubatso, ndiye wakasimba.
\p
\v 16 Mukadzi muuya anokudzwa; Vakasimba vanochengeta pfuma dzavo.
\p
\v 17 Munhu ane ngoni, anoitira mweya wake zvakanaka;
\s Asi asina tsitsi anotambudza nyama yake.
\p
\v 18 Wakaipa anopiwa mubayiro wokunyengedzera;
\s Asi anokusha kururama achawana mubayiro wazvokwadi.
\p
\v 19 Kururama kwazvokwadi kunoisa kuupenyu;
\s Asi anotevera zvakaipa, anovinga rufu rwake.
\p
\v 2 ° Vane mwoyo yakatsauka vanonyangadza Jehovha;
\s Asi vanofamba nenzira yakarurama vanomufadza.
\p
\v 21 Zvirokwazvo, wakaipa haangakoni kurohwa;
\s Asi vana vavakarurama vacharwirwa.
\p
\v 22 Sezvakaita chindori chendarama mumhino dzenguruve,
\s Ndizvo zvakaita mukadzi wakanaka kumeso asina kungwara.
\p
\v 23 Zvinodikanwa navakarurama zvakanaka bedzi;
\s Asi vakaipa vanomirirwa nokutsamwa.
\p
\v 24 Mumwe ariko anoparadzira, achiwedzerwa;
\s Uye ariko anonyima zvaakafanira kupa,
\s asi zvinongomushaisa.
\p
\v 25 Chipavurire achakodzwa;
\s Uye anodiridza achadiridzwawo.
\p
\v 26 Unonyima zviyo, vanhu vachamutuka;
\s Asi mikomborero ichava pamusoro woanozvitengesa.
\p
\v 27 Anoshingairira zvinhu zvakanaka, anotsvaka zvinofadza;
\s Asi anotsvaka zvakashata, achasvikirwawo nazvo.
\p
\v 28 Anovimba nepfuma yake, achawa; Asi vakarurama vachanaka
\s seshizha nyoro.
\p
\v 29 Anotambudza imba yake, achagara nhaka yemhepo;
\s Benzi richava muranda woano mwoyo wakachenjera.
\s Zvibereko zvowakarurama muti womupenyu;
\s Unobata mweya yavanhu ndiye wakachenjera.
\p
\v 31 Tarirai, wakarurama achapiwa mubayiro panyika;
\s Ndoda wakaipa nomutadzi!
